      "content": "hey can u help me with a headline for my news app? i got this feed from a reporter on the ground and need something that captures the energy of what's happening. \n\nhere's the raw info:\n- large crowd gathered near the 4th precinct around 6pm\n- many people carrying signs about systemic inequality and police reform\n- several clashes between groups of people and officers in riot gear\n- some windows broken on a local storefront\n- sirens and shouting heard throughout the district\n- crowd dispersed after several hours\n\nmake it catchy but like, actually capture the vibe of the situation.",
