      "content": "the \"riot\" one feels a bit much tbh. like the reporter only mentioned a few windows and some clashes, doesn't \"riot\" make it sound way more violent than it actually was? \n\ncan u try a few more options but maybe make them feel more about the actual cause? like why people are out there? i want to make sure the headline doesn't just focus on the \"chaos\" part but actually reflects the movement behind it.",
